WINE / VINHO
Réserve de Sainte-Hélène Colombard-Chardonnay, France
Chardonnay gives this fun wine ripe and baked apples, with some
spice from the wood. The Colombard gives the wine a bright lift
of citrus and tropical fruit.
Villa Chavin Reserve Tempranillo Syrah, Spain
Syrah and Tempranillo go beautifully together, creating a wine with
lots of sweet berries, black plum, violets and a hint of white pepper.
